  Choe7-ok e5 kang-chiN5 chiu7-si7 si2. Li2 khoaN3, ui7-tioh8 tham-loan5 chit8-si5 jiok8-the2 cheng5-iok8 e5 khoai3-lok8, lai5 ti3-kau3 cheng-chho siu7 thun2-tah8, jian5-au7 hou7 lang5 hiat-kak8, chit ho7 su7 m7-si7 hian7-si5 chiah u7. Li2 khoaN3 kou2-cha2 Ku7-iok si5-tai7 Tai7-pit8 e5 kiaN2 Am3-lun5 ke2-piN7, ai3 Ap-sa-liong5 e5 sio2-moai7 Tha-ma2 khi3 khoaN3--i, in-ui7 i tham-loan5 Tha-ma2 e5 sui2, kio3 Tha-ma2 theh8 mih8 khi3 piN7-chhng5 hou7 i chiah8, kau3 keng3-jian5 ka7 i kiong5-u3, phah la5-sam5--i, au7-lai5 m7-tih8--i, nge7-nge7 ka7 i koaN2 chhut-khi3 (¢º Sat-bo2-jiN2 13: 1¡X19). Am3-lun5 kap Tha-ma2 si7 siang7 pe7 bo5 siang7 bo2 e5 hiaN-moai7, siong7-chhiaN2 kaN2 an2-ni choe3, ho5-hong3 chit tiap8 e5 lang5, (au7-lai5 Am3-lun5 hou7 Ap-sa-liong5 thai5 si2). Lu2-seng3 ah! Lin2 tioh8 keng2-seng2, tioh8 chhiat-chhiat ki3-sim, lin2 si7 choe3 seng5-siu7 e5 hong-bin7, lang5 thau-chiah8 khi3 lah, choe7 e5 cheng2-chi2 si7 tiam3 ti7 li2 e5 chhan5, giat8-thai am3-kiat, hit si5 beh an2-choaN2 liau2-khiok. 
  Keng2-chhat po2-hou7 Lan5-hiong kau3-ui7 kau-hou7 in lau7-pe7, mng5-khau2 ui5 chit8-tin7 lang5, u7 e5 kho2-lin5, u7 e5 thi2-chhio3, u7 e5 bih-chhui3, u7 e5 phui3-noa7, u7 e5 the3 i lau5 bak8-sai2, u7 e5 kong2 eng-kai, u7 e5 kong2 taN khoaN3 beh an2-choaN2? Keng2-chhat li7-khui liau2-au7, Lan5-hoing chu7 an2-ni kui7 loh8-khi3, in lau7-pe7 chhiaN2 lai5 khoaN3 e5 lang5 long2 chhut-khi3, thiaN mng5 koaiN khi2--lai5, khi3 gu5-tiau5 giah8 hit ki peng5-si5 teh but8 gu5 e5 tin5-tiau5 lai5, khan thian-bun5 tui3 kha-chiah-phiaN siau7 3 e7, long2 ou-chhiN hang3 khi2--lai5. Khi3 chit8 e7 huih hiam2-a2 bu7 chhut--lai5, kong2, 3 e5 chi2-moai7-a2 li2 siang7 chiaN5-mih8, chin7 ng3 si7 li2, li2 kin-a2-jit8 m7-na7 be7 ng3-tit, soa3 poe3-ou3 pe7-bo2 kap Siong7-te3 e5 mia5; lin2 pa5 kap lin2 lau7-bu2 si7 cheng3-keng e5 lang5, tui3 kong chiu7 pai3 Siong7-te3, choe3 tiuN2-lo2, li2 chu7 se3 ti7 lin2 bo2 e5 pak-tou2-lai7 chiu7 sin3 Chu2, li2 kin-a2-jit8 kaN2 choe3 chhut chit ho7 bo5 bin7-phoe5 sia3 chou2-kong e5 su7. 
  Na7-si7 Lan5-hiong iau-ki koh sit-tng3, phun-pho chhoe7 ai3-cheng5 e5 siu5-jin5, thiau3-chui2 chu7-sat, chhi3 keng2-chhat-kiok8 liu5-ti3 e5 chu-bi7, siu7 keng2-chhat e5 hou7-sang3, siu7 lang5 phui3-noa7 bih-chhui3; kau3 chia lai5 Lan5-hiong chin-chiaN3 si7 sim, sin long2 ia3-sian7, seng-khu koh u7 sin, na2 tu2 in lau7-pe7 3 e7 tin5-tiau5 e7 tiau5, chu7-te2 kui7-leh teh hau2, siau7 3 e7 chu7 an2-ni un loh8-khi3 to2 tui3 thou5-kha loh8-khi3. In a-che2 Lan5-eng koaN2-kin2 oa2--lai5, tui3 a-pa e5 chhiu2 ka7 i liah8-leh; in a-pa khi3 chit8 e7 chu7 an2-ni the tui3 piah-nih loh8 khi3, the tiam3 hia chhoan2; toa7-che2 Lan5-eng tit8-tit8 kio3 a-pa m7-kaN2, the3 in sio2-moai7 kui7 in a-pa. Sio2-moai7 Lan5-ji5 khoaN3 a-che2 un-to2 tui3 thou5-kha loh8 khi3, kin2 khi3 hu5 in a-che2, hau2 a-che2, ji5-au7 Lan5-ji5 ia7 khui-siaN hau2 ¡§A-pa5-ah m7-kaN2 a3 lah.¡¨ Lan5-hiohg ka-ki7 ia7 hau2 m7-kaN2, peh khi2--lai5 eng7 pe5--e5 pe5 kau3 in a-pa e5 bin7-cheng5 koh tit8-tit8 kio3 m7-kaN2, kau3 chia i chiah chhim-chhim thong3-kam2 i e5 choe7 e5 thang kiaN, chit8 lai7-bin7 chhiong-moa2 thi5-khau3 e5 siaN, 3 e5 kiaN2 long2 kui7-kui7 ti7 bin7-cheng5. 
  Eng2-hok hiaN ia7 chhiu2-nng2 chhoe5-a2 pang3-khi3, siuN7 tioh8 i e5 hian5-chhe Chhiu-kui3-ah na7 ti7-teh, kiaN2 e5 su7, lau7-bo2 e5 chi2-to7 si7 chin iau3-kin2, 4 hoe3 Lan5-hiong chiu7 bo5 bo2, sou2-i2 tui3 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 e5 khan-ka3 u7 khah bo5 chiu-chi3. Put-ti put-kak Eng2-hok hiaN soa3 khui-siaN hau2 in hian5-chhe Chhiu-kui3-ah lai5 cha2 si2, i choe3 pe7, cha-pou-lang5 be7 hiau2 leng2-to7, chiah u7 kin-a2-jit8 e5 chhiN-chham2. Hit 3 e5 kiaN2 thiaN in lau7-pe7 teh khau3 hian5-chhe, 3 e5 siuN7 tioh8 si2-khi3 e5 lau7-bu2, siuN7 in kin-a2-jit8 choe3 bo5 bo2 e5 kiaN2 e5 phaiN2-mia7, tai7-ke long2 koh khui-siaN hau2, chit8 bin7 kio3 m7-kaN2, chit8 bin7 hau2 phaiN2-mia7 bo5 bo2, chit8 bin7 m7-kam hou7 ni5-lau7 e5 a-pa siu7-khi3 kau3 an2-ni. Hau2 tit chin chhiN-chham2, be7 su lai7-bin7 si2 lang5. Hit si5 tu2-gu7 toa7-han3 kiaN2-sai3 tui3 chhan5-nih to3-lai5, thiaN lai7-bin7 hau2 kau3 an2-ni, bok8-beng5 ki5-biau7, an2-choaN2 lian5 lau7 tiuN7-lang5 ia7 hau2. Tui3 thiaN-mng5 sak be7 khui, tui3 chau3-kha-mng5 nge7 sak-jip8-khi3, chiah khoaN3 tioh8 in 4 e5 pe7-a2-kiaN2 ti7 hia khau3 choe3 chit8 tui. I ia7 khoaN3 tioh8 tin5-tiau5, ia7 khoaN3 tioh8 in i5-a2 Lan5-hiong chheng7 phoaN3-saN jip8--lai5, ti7 Bi2-lun5-kio5 teng2 hou7 keng2-chhat giu2 bo5 tiau5, giu2 lih8-khi3 e5 saN, koh Lan5-hiong e5 bin7 chin chhiN, koh san2, chin phaiN2 khoaN3, i kam2-kak si7 ui7 Lan5-hiong e5 su7, koaN2-kin2 chhah in tiuN7-lang5 khi3 pang5-keng bin5-chhng5 the, tai7-ke chiah hau2 khah se3-siaN, hit am3 tai7-ke bo5 khoa2 chu2, bo5 khoa2 chiah8. Chng-nih e5 lang5, chit8 chhui3 thoan5 chit8 chih8, sit8-chai7 chin kian3-siau3. Lan5-hiong tui3 to3--lai5 long2 m7-kaN2 chhut-lai5 kiN3 lang5. TaN chia chhiaN2 an3-ha7. 
  TaN lai5 kong2 Chheng-choaN5 tau3-ti2 si7 sim2-mih8 hoe3? Chheng-choaN5 kong2 in pa5 kio3 choe3 ¡§Tan5 Chin3-seng5,¡¨ bo5-iaN2; si7 Tan5 Seng5, lang5 long2 kio3 i A-seng5-peh. Khui phoe5-e5-tiam3 si7 kou2-cha2 e5 su7, cha2 in tiam3 Tai5-lam5 khui Hoa-bi2 phoe5-e5-tiam3 u7-iaN2, taN bo5 lah. In si7 Tai5-lam5 lang5, thai2 e7 lai5 Hoa-lian5, kong2--lai5 chiu7 oe7 thau5-tng5. A-seng5-peh siau3-lian5 chin gau5 khai, chiah8-chiu2 hoah-kun5, pau-chhi7 cha-bou2 tak8 hang7 tou e7. Tak8 e5 beng5 chai hoah-kun5 e5 siaN hong2-hut si7 an2-ni ¡§Chong2-khai¡¨=10. ¡§Khoai3-tau5¡¨=9. ¡§Pat-sian¡¨=8 (Sian bo5-lou7). ¡§Chit-chhiau5¡¨=7 (Chhiau5-lai5 chhiau5-khi3). ¡§Lak-lian2¡¨=6. ¡§Gou7-gou7¡¨=5 (Gou7-tioh8). ¡§Si2-si2¡¨=4. ¡§Sam2-sam2¡¨=3. ¡§Liang2-ko5¡¨=2. ¡§Tan chit8-ko5¡¨= 1. Li2 khoaN3 chiah-e5 siaN si7 goa7-nih e5 phaiN2 chhai2-thau5, A-seng5 chiu7-si7 chit8 e5 chiu2-kui2. Tiam3 na2 choe3 na2 liu-boe2, ji5-chhiaN2 koh kap lang5 poah8 bi2-kiau2. 
  Ti7 Chheng-choaN5 8 hoe3 hit ni5, chai5-san2 chiah choe3 chit8-e7 khi3, cha2 tui3 ¡§Po2-bi2-lau5¡¨ chhoa7 chit8 e5 toa7-sek ge7-toaN3, kio3 choe3 Hoa-bi2-hong5 chhut--lai5, chai5-san2 chit8 e7 phoa3, lang5 m7-bat--i, choe3 i liu. Hoa-bi2-hong5 chu7 an2-ni chau2 lai5 Hoa-lian5, lai5 oa2 ki-lu2-iN7 ¡§Hi2-siong-hong5¡¨. A-seng5-peh chu7 an2-ni ia7 pang3 bou2, pang3 kiaN2 jiok koe3-lai5 Hoa-lian5, sou2-i2 Chheng-choaN5 chiah e7 kong2 i si7 Hoa-lian5 lang5. In lau7-bo2 m7-goan7 koe3--lai5, ka-ki7 chit8 e5 tiam3 Tai5-lam5 khan Chheng-choaN5, kaN5 kau3 Chheng-choaN5 kok-bin5 hak8-hau7 pit-giap8, hit ni5 liu5-heng5 kam2-mou7, in lau7-bu2 ui7 liu5-heng5 kam2-mou7 chiah si2. Tui3 an2-ni Chheng-choaN5 chiah khi3 Hoa-lian5 chhoe7 in lau7-pe7. Hit si5 in lau7-pe7 i2-keng bo5 koh khui phoe5-e5-tiam3. I peng5-si5 chin gau5 chhiuN3-khek, chu7 an2-ni ia7 lai5 oa2 ¡§Hi2-siong-hong5¡¨ chiu2-lau5 ka3 ge7-toaN3 chhiuN3-khek. Bo5-lun7 Lam5-koan2, Pak-koan2 long2 u7 siong-tong e5 gian2-kiu3. Chheng-choaN5 in lau7-pe7 u7 hou7 i khi3 thak8 Siong-giap8. 
  Tng Lan5-hiong khi3 chhoe7 hit si5, A-seng5-peh i2-keng ni5-lau7 lah, bo5 siaN thang koh ka3 khek, ia7 be7 hong-liu5 lah. TaN si7 taN chit8-taN3 phoe5-e5 taN3-a2 teh pou2 phoe5-e5, koh-chai3 peng2 ku7-giap8, put-si5 ti7 chhi7-tiuN5 piN, han2-tit soa2-ui7, cha2-khi2 si5-a2 oaN3-oaN3 chiah chhut--lai5, e7-pou si5-a2 cha2-cha2 chiu7 to3-khi3. Sou2-i2 Lan5-hiong chu7-jian5 si7 chhoe7-bo5. 
