  12. SiuN ban7 lah
  An2-choaN2 kong2 Lan5-hiong si7 hou7 lang5 kham3 tiam3 ang3 lai7. An2-choaN2 Chheng-choaN5 phoa3-piN7, kong-si e7 beh ka7 i chhut hui3 ti7-liau5, nng7 le2-pai3 chiu7 e7 tit chhut-iN7, an2-choaN2 oan7 kau3 saN le2-pai3, kong-si ia7 be7 ke-oe7. Goan5-in ti7 chia, chiu7-si7 i si7 kong-si keng-li2 e5 bi7-lai5 e5 kiaN2-sai3, chu7 cha2 chiu7 i2-keng teng3-hun lah. Na7-si7 an2-ni thai2 e7 kap Lan5-hiong hiah chhin-jiat8. He si7 chhai2-hoe-phang. Bit8-phang teh chhai2-hoe, chit8-lui2 hoe koe3 chit8-lui2 hoe e5 chhiu2-toaN7, bit8-phang ui7 beh chhai2 hoe e5 bit8, tak8 pai2 i tou si7 kap hoe chin chhin-bit8, m7-koan2 seN-si2, ham7 sin kap mia7 tit8-tit8 tui3 hoe-sim chng3 loh8-khi3, bo5 sioh i kap hoe saN-chim e5 chhin-bit8. Bit8 chhai2 liau2 e7 koh lai5 a2-be7? Be7 lah, hiat-kak8--li2, lian5 oat8-thau5 tou bo5, choe3 i khi3, thi2-sit8 poe hou7 li2 jiok. 
  Chheng-choaN5 sim-te2 na2 u7-iaN2 teh ai3 Lan5-hiong leh. I sou2 pheng3-tiaN7 e5 bi7-hun-chhe sui-jian5 bo5 Lan5-hiong e5 sui2, m7-ku2 u7 chai5, se3, lek8; i ti7 kong-si e5 te7-ui7 si7 kho3 in bi7-lai5 e5 tiuN7-lang5 e5 se3, in bou2 e5 au7-thau5 si7 i e5 au7-piah-soaN. I na2 u7 khoaN3-tioh8 soaN-lai7 e5 chhoan-kou. Chhau2-te7 kou-niu5 sui-jian5 si7 thak8-koe3 chhou-tiong, ti7 peN7-iN7 hiah ku2, u7 san2-po5, hou7-su7 e5 chu-keh. Na7-si7 chu7 se3 sin3 Chu2, pai3 Siong7-te3, long2 si7 kap pai3 Siong7-te3 e5 lang5 kau-poe5 chhut-jip8, seng5-sit8, bo5 oan-khiau, tit8-tit8, tak8 hang7 khoai3 sin3--lang5. Chheng-choaN5 e5 chhui3 be7 su koa3 siang e5 chih8, sian3 tit Lan5-hiong hi7-a2 phak-phak. Koh in2-iu2 lu2-sek e5 lau2-chhiu2, Lan5-hiong chit8 chiah na2 toa7-ti, kui2-ku3-a2 oe7 ka7 i ngiau, kui2-hang7-a2 mih8 choe3 bi2-khng ka7 i soah loh8-khi3, chiu7 toe3 lang5 tit8-tit8 kiaN5. 
  An2-choaN2 thang kap lang5 iok-sok siong-hoe7, an2-choaN2 thang kap lam5-seng3 che7 sio-kheh, thau5-khak ti7 lam5-seng3 e5 heng-cheng5. Koh thang toe3 lang5 khi3 lu2-sia7, kaN2 toe3 lang5 peh kau3 4 lau5, koh khui pang5-keng, chi2-u7 nng7 e5, mng5 so2 khi2-lai5, so2-si5 te7 tiam3 cha-pou-lang5 e5 te7-a2. Koh khi3 hit chhut e7 chhong3 sim2-mih8? Si7 pi2 khoaN3 hoe2 khah beng5. Kai si2, chin-chiaN3 kai si2. Kau3 hia beh chau2 bo5 lou7 lah. M7-si7, kau3 hit chun7 be7 siuN7 beh chau2 lah, hit si5 e5 sim si7 chhi-be5 chui3-chiu2 e5 chong7-thai3, sim bang5--khi3 lah. Chu7 thau5 ti7 i-iN7 e5 si5, am3-si5 m7-si7 tioh8 i lun5-tioh8 tong-tit8, chiu7 m7 eng-kai khi3 kou3 i, beh khi3 eng-kai chio phoaN7. Chin-chiaN3 si7 hou7 kui2 be5, chui2-kui2 teh kio3 Pai2-sui7 chiu7-si7 an2-ni. 
  Chin-chiaN3 si7 hou7-hoe2 siuN ban7 lah. Chheng-choaN5 chhut-iN7 bo5 loa7-ku2, chiu7 kap keng-li2 e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 kiat-hun. PoaN3 chio-chhoa7, in-ui7 sin-niu5 hit peng5 e5 sio2-ti7 iau2 chin se3-han3, sou2-i2 phin2 hou7 in chio, kau3 sio2-ti7 toa7-han3 chiah chhut-khi3, sou2-i2 it-chhe3 e5 kiat-hun-hui3 long2 in tiuN7-lang5 chi-li2, chin-chiaN3 si7 tit chhe-ka-chai5 e5 ho2-un7-ji5. Chham2 e5 chi2-u7 si7 peh8 hou7 lang5 chau-that, le2-choa2, chhu3-lu2 po2-kui3 e5 seN3-mia7 hou7 lang5 thiah phoa3 koh hou7 lang5 hiat-kak8, giat8-thai koh am3-kiat, si7 chhau3-chian7 e5 ku7-hoe3, choe3 pou3 tat8-chiN5, choe3 saN m7-tat8 chiN5. TaN beh an2-choaN2? 
  Kan-ta Chheng-choaN5 teh song2-khoai3, teh tit chhe-ka-chai5. Na7-si7 ho2 keng2 bo5 ku2, Chheng-choaN5 kiat-hun bo5 loa7-ku2, Tiong Jit8 Lou5-kau-kio5 su7-pian3 hoat-seng, keh-ni5 e5 4 goeh8 chhe 5, Chheng-choaN5 e5 ang5-toaN-a2 kau3 lah. Chiu7-si7 siu7 Jit8-pun2 cheng3-hu2 e5 Liok8-kun-seng2 tiau3 i khi3 choe3 thong-ek8. Tai7-seng khi3 Hoa5-pak, tong-si5 kong2 ho7-choe3 Pak Chi, au7-lai5 toe3 kun tit8-tit8 choan2-chian3 kau3 Hoa5-lam5. Tng Se3-kai3 te7 2 hoe5 tai7-chian3 lian5-hoat e5 si5, chiu7 choan2-chian3 khi3 Lu7-song3. Khi2-thau5 ti7 Ma-ni-lah, au7-lai5 ia7 bat kau3 Phek-iau5, hit si5 Jit8-kun lian5-chian3 lian5-seng3, tui3 ji7-teng2-peng tit8-tit8 seng, seng kau3 chun2-ui3. Se3-thau5 chin ho2, chheng7 kun-chong hip siong7 kia3 to3-lai5 hou7 in bou2. Bak8-chit8-nih koe3 5, 6 ni5. Siok8-gu2 an2-ni kong2, ¡§Chun5-oan5 kau3 tak8 e5 kang2-khau2 tou u7 in chhu3.¡¨ Chheng-choaN5 kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7 ia7-si7 an2-ni. 
  Tong-si5 Jit8-pun2 choe3 chian3-seng3-kun e5 kun-ki2 sit8-chai7 chin kian3-siau3, to3-chhu3 chhi2-ti7 leng5-jiok8 lang5 e5 hu7-lu2. Chong2-si7 li2 ia7 m7-bian2 siuN7 i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 ti7 chhu3-nih si7 choat8-tui3 e5 cheng-chiat. Kiat-hun bo5 chit8 ni5, iau2-boe7 khioh gin2-na2, tng chheng-chhun, si7 se3-siok8 bo5 sin3 to7-li2 e5 ka-teng5, ti7 Tai5-pak chhia-hoa5 e5 sou2-chai7, li2 siuN7 i kiam2 e7 tiam7-tiam7 lai5 chiu2 khang-pang5. Sou2-i2 i ia7 thau kiaN5 i e5 lou7. 
  Kau3 chian3-cheng e5 hou7-poaN3, hut-jian5 Chheng-choaN5 e5 siau-sit chu7 an2-ni tng7-khi3 lah, m7-si7 tng7 tiap-a2-ku2, si7 eng2-oan2 e5 tng7-khi3. Tui3 siau-sit tng7-khi3 liau2-au7, koh hiah ku2 bo5 tng2-lai5, put-ti put-kak Chheng-choaN5 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 toe3 lang5 khi3 lah. In seN-pe7 ia7 khoaN3-phoa3, bo5 chhap, pang3 hou7 in cha-bou2-kiaN2 chu7-iu5. TaN chia chhiaN2 an3-ha7. Khah iau3-kin2 lan2 koh lai5 siuN7 Lan5-hiong e5 su7. 
